#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:4
msgid "I"
msgstr "I"

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:9
msgid "It was a dark time..."
msgstr "Es war eine dunkle Zeit..."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:12
msgid ""
"Three warlords returned to Alheirra to request more troops to support the "
"battleground in the north."
msgstr ""
"Drei Kriegsherren kehrten nach Alheirra zurück, um mehr Truppen zur "
"Unterstützung der Schlachtreihen im Norden anzufordern."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:15
msgid ""
"One of them, Thenaken of Wizlud, had watched the arising of the dark powers "
"in the north for a long time an felt that the time of action had come now. "
"He arranged a meeting with the marshal of Alheirra and let the two younger, "
"less experienced lords go on a quest for men to go to the battlegrounds in "
"the north."
msgstr ""
"Einer von ihnen, Thenaken von Wizlud, hatte das Erwachen der dunklen Mächte "
"im Norden lange Zeit beobachtet und spürte, dass die Zeit des Handelns nun "
"gekommen war. Er verabredete ein Treffen mit dem Marschall von Alheirra und "
"ließ die beiden jüngeren, weniger erfahrenen Lehnsherren nach Männern "
"suchen, die an die Schlachtfelder im Norden reisen würden."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Three days later four graves were dug, which were saying: 'Thenaken of "
"Wizlud', 'Alberrac of Tinderah', 'Oraidir of Jeren' and 'a-Hamerrad of "
"Alheirra'."
msgstr ""
"Drei Tage später wurden vier Gräber ausgehoben, auf denen stand: 'Thenaken "
"von Wizlud', 'Alberrac von Tinderah', 'Oraidir von Jeren' und 'a-Hamerrad "
"von Alheirra'."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:21
msgid ""
"We are in Wizlud, home of the deceased warlord Thenaken. Thesandir, his son, "
"tries bitterly to reconquer the half of Wizlud which fell into the hands of "
"nordic bandits."
msgstr ""
"Wir befinden uns in Wizlud, der Heimat des verstorbenen Kriegsherren "
"Thenaken. Thesandir, sein Sohn, versucht erbittert, die Hälfte von Wizlud "
"zurückzuerobern, die in die Hände von nordischen Banditen gefallen ist."

#. [side]: id=thesandir, type=Grand Marshal
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:27 sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:124
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:205 sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:324
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:423 sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:538
msgid "Thesandir"
msgstr "Thesandir"

#. [side]: id=lieutenant, type=Fugitive
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:39
msgid "Lieutenant"
msgstr "Leutnant"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:52
msgid "Crush the bandits' lieutenant."
msgstr "Vernichte den Leutnant der Banditen."

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:56 sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:152
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:360 sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:470
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:50 sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:141
msgid "Death."
msgstr "Tod."

#. [message]: speaker=thesandir
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:65
msgid ""
"We will show you what happens if you enter the territory of the warlords of "
"Alheirra, bandit rabble!"
msgstr ""
"Wir werden euch zeigen, was passiert, wenn ihr das Territorium der "
"Kriegsherren von Alheirra betretet, Banditenpack!"

#. [message]: speaker=lieutenant
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:69
msgid "Oh, yes? I'm so afraid, worm!"
msgstr "Oh, ja? Ich habe solche Angst, Wurm!"

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:97
msgid ""
"After Thesandir, son of Thenaken, defeated the bandits he rushed to Alheirra "
"to report to the marshal."
msgstr ""
"Nachdem Thesandir, Sohn des Thenaken, die Banditen besiegt hatte, eilte er "
"nach Alheirra, um dem Marschall Bericht zu erstatten."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:100
msgid ""
"Finally, he was told by a merchant that the marshal of Alheirra and three "
"warlords, one of them his father, had been murdered."
msgstr ""
"Schließlich erfuhr er von einem Händler, dass der Marschall von Alheirra und "
"drei Kriegsherren, einer von ihnen sein Vater, ermordet worden waren."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:103
msgid ""
"In agony, he made his way to his good friend Sinisar, who had a store in "
"Alheirra, to listen to his advice."
msgstr ""
"In tiefer Trauer machte er sich auf den Weg zu seinem guten Freund Sinisar, "
"der einen Laden in Alheirra hatte, um seinen Rat anzuhören."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:106
msgid ""
"But also Sinisar was dead. He lay with slashed throat on the counter and "
"stared at Thesandir with an empty glance."
msgstr ""
"Aber auch Sinisar war tot. Er lag mit aufgeschlitzter Kehle auf dem Tresen "
"und starrte Thesandir mit leerem Blick an."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:109
msgid ""
"After Thesandir had wandered through Alheirra for long hours, one of his "
"guards found him and brought him back to Wizlud, where he had to overtake "
"his father's business."
msgstr ""
"Nachdem Thesandir lange Stunden durch Alheirra geirrt war, brachte ihn eine "
"seiner Wachen zurück nach Wizlud, wo er die Geschäfte seines Vaters "
"übernehmen musste."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:112
msgid ""
"Soon a new marshal for Alheirra was elected and further the fights in the "
"north were raging. But it seemed like the opposing forces were smashed by "
"the well-qualified and disciplined guards of Alheirra."
msgstr ""
"Bald wurde ein neuer Marschall für Alheirra gewählt und die Kämpfe im Norden "
"tobten weiter. Aber es schien, dass die gegnerischen Truppen von den gut "
"ausgebildeten und disziplinierten Wachen Alheirras zerschlagen wurden."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:115
msgid ""
"When it became public that important figures taking place in the fights were "
"killed at night, Thesandir could not leave it at that."
msgstr ""
"Als es öffentlich wurde, dass wichtige Figuren, die an den Kämpfen "
"teilnahmen, in der Nacht umgebracht wurden, konnte Thesandir es nicht dabei "
"belassen."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:118
msgid ""
"He traveled northwards. Already ahead from the battlegrounds skirmishes took "
"place, which however ended fast in favor of Alheirra. Thesandir of Wizlud "
"reached Necliz, the severely contested fortress in the north."
msgstr ""
"Er reiste nordwärts. Schon vor den Schlachtfeldern fanden Kämpfe statt, die "
"jedoch schnell zugunsten von Alheirra ein Ende fanden. Thesandir von Wizlud "
"erreichte Necliz, die schwer umkämpfte Festung im Norden."

#. [side]: id=captain, type=Fugitive
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:136
msgid "Captain"
msgstr "Hauptmann"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:148
msgid "Crush the bandits' captain."
msgstr "Vernichte den Hauptmann der Banditen."

#. [message]: speaker=thesandir
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:161
msgid "We will not let the nort fall into the hands of bandits!"
msgstr "Wir werden den Norden nicht in die Hände von Banditen fallen lassen!"

#. [message]: speaker=captain
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:165
msgid ""
"Barely a few hairs of the beard but already wants to play with the big ones."
msgstr ""
"Kaum aus den Windeln herausgewachsen, möchte aber schon mit den Großen "
"spielen."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:193
msgid ""
"After hard fights the captain could be distinguished, which was to a big "
"part credit of Wizlud's guards. The soldiers noticed quickly that Thesandir "
"was a skilled leader and promised him loyalty to death."
msgstr ""
"Nach einem harten Kampf konnte der Hauptmann vernichtet werden, was zu einem "
"großen Teil der Verdienst von Thesandirs Wachen war. Die Soldaten merkten "
"schnell, dass Thesandir ein fähiger Anführer war und versprachen ihm Treue "
"bis in den Tod."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:196
msgid ""
"Necliz could be held as long as the rare attacks could not do wreak havoc. "
"But merely, the peace was of short while."
msgstr ""
"Necliz konnte so lange gehalten werden, wie die spärlichen Angriffe keinen "
"großen Schaden anrichteten. Aber der Frieden war nur von kurzer Dauer."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:199
msgid ""
"Two months after Thesandir had arrived in the north the bandits reconquered "
"Necliz in a nightly assault. Thesandir's soldiers were forced back "
"southwards until they could hold a fortress named Shizad. Now Thesandir had "
"to fight back the bandits if he wanted to hold the north."
msgstr ""
"Zwei Monate, nachdem Thesandir im Norden angekommen war, übernahmen die "
"Banditen Necliz in einem nächtlichen Angriff. Thesandirs Soldaten wurden "
"südwärts gedrängt, bis sie eine Festung namens Shizad halten konnten. Nun "
"musste Thesandir die Banditen zurückschlagen, wenn er den Norden halten "
"wollte."

#. [unit]: id=zarim, type=Halberdier
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:215
msgid "Zarim"
msgstr "Zarim"

#. [side]: id=major, type=Fugitive
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:226
msgid "Major"
msgstr "Major"

#. [unit]: id=clguard, type=Highwayman
#. [unit]: id=mjguard, type=Highwayman
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:235 sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:345
msgid "Guard"
msgstr "Wache"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:246
msgid "Crush the bandits' major."
msgstr "Vernichte den Major der Banditen."

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:250
msgid "Tod."
msgstr "Tod."

#. [message]: speaker=zarim
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:259
msgid "My lord, I am Zarim of Shizad. I will support you."
msgstr "Mein Herr, ich bin Zarim von Shizad. Ich werde Euch unterstützen."

#. [message]: speaker=thesandir
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:263
msgid "Fine. We need every help."
msgstr "Gut. Wir brauchen jede Hilfe."

#. [message]: speaker=major
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:267
msgid "We'll break you, one more or less!"
msgstr "Wir werden euch brechen, einer mehr oder weniger!"

#. [message]: speaker=zarim
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:295
msgid "Ha, the guard is dead! Now it will be easy!"
msgstr "Ha, die Wache ist tot! Jetzt wird es einfach sein!"

#. [message]: speaker=major
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:299
msgid "You can't defeat us!"
msgstr "Ihr könnt uns nicht besiegen!"

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:309
msgid ""
"After Shizad was relieved from the bandits Thesandir moved on to the north "
"to tell the genearal the enemy had gained strength since beleaguering Wizlud."
msgstr ""
"Nachdem Shizad von den Banditen erlöst wurde, reiste Thesandir weiter in den "
"Norden, um dem General mitzuteilen, dass der Feind seit der Belagerung von "
"Wizlud stärker geworden war."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:312
msgid ""
"When he arrived at the battlegrounds, he heard that the general had been "
"assaulted. He had died in the morning."
msgstr ""
"Als er an den Schlachtreihen ankam, hörte er, dass der General überfallen "
"wurde. Er war in den Morgenstunden gestorben."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:315
msgid ""
"Thesandir went into the tavern to find out more just as the horn resounded. "
"All soldiers hurried outside and put on their armor. An envoy delivered the "
"message that Jeren, the fortress of one of the warlords having accompanied "
"Thenaken to Alheirra, was harassed by bandits whose power exceeded all prior "
"forces."
msgstr ""
"Thesandir ging in die Taverne, um mehr herauszufinden, als gerade das Horn "
"schallte. Alle Soldaten eilten nach draußen und legten die Rüstungen an. Ein "
"Bote brachte die Nachricht, dass Jeren, die Festung eines der Kriegsherren, "
"die Thenaken nach Alheirra begleitet hatten, von Banditen belagert wurde, "
"deren Stärke über alle vorherigen hinausging."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:318
msgid ""
"The castle Jeren at the icy coast was on the verge of defeat when "
"Thesandir's army arrived and granted them a saving delay."
msgstr ""
"Die Burg Jeren an der eisigen Küste stand an der Schwelle zur Niederlage, "
"als Thesandirs Armee eintraf und ihnen einen rettenden Vorsprung verschaffte."

#. [side]: id=colonel, type=Fugitive
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:336
msgid "Colonel"
msgstr "Oberst"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:356
msgid "Crush the bandits' colonel."
msgstr "Vernichte den Oberst der Banditen."

#. [message]: speaker=thesandir
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:369
msgid "We will punch you back to your caves!"
msgstr "Wir werden euch zurück in eure Höhlen schlagen!"

#. [message]: speaker=colonel
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:373
msgid "You don't know which powers you dare to play with, fools!"
msgstr "Ihr wisst nicht, mit welchen Mächten ihr zu spielen wagt, Narren!"

#. [message]: speaker=thesandir
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:401
msgid "Keep it up, men!"
msgstr "Macht weiter, Männer!"

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:411
msgid ""
"The victory of Jeren gave new hope to the civics in the north and actually "
"the fights went better than ever. The bandit peoples were pushed back far "
"northwards and the big region around Bashid was recaptured."
msgstr ""
"Der Sieg von Jeren gab den Bürgern im Norden neue Hoffnung und tatsächlich "
"gingen die Kämpfe besser denn je. Die Banditenvölker wurden weit nordwärts "
"zurückgedrängt und die große Region um Bashid wurde zurückerobert."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:414
msgid ""
"But after some time, the bandits hit back. In Bashid finally, six months "
"after Thesandir's arrival, the defenders of the north were facing the "
"bandits' marshal's army."
msgstr ""
"Aber nach einiger Zeit schlugen die Banditen zurück. In Bashid schließlich, "
"sechs Monate nach Thesandirs Ankunft, standen die Verteidiger des Nordens "
"der Armee des Marschalls der Banditen gegenüber."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:417
msgid "This skirmish would decide about the north's fate."
msgstr "Diese Schlacht würde über das Schicksal des Nordens entscheiden."

#. [unit]: id=nasir, type=Halberdier
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:434
msgid "Nasir"
msgstr "Nasir"

#. [side]: id=marshal, type=Fugitive
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:445
msgid "Marshal"
msgstr "Marschall"

#. [unit]: id=msguard, type=Highwayman
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:455
msgid "Sentinel"
msgstr "Erzwache"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:466
msgid "Crush the bandits' marshall and lead Alheirra to victory."
msgstr "Vernichte den Marschall der Banditen und führe Alheirra zum Sieg."

#. [message]: speaker=nasir
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:479
msgid ""
"My lord, I have heard about your victory of Jeren. You are a hero! Thus I "
"provide my Iron Maulers to you and will ride into the battle at your side! "
"For Alheirra!"
msgstr ""
"Mein Herr, ich hörte von Eurem Sieg von Jeren. Ihr seid ein Held! Daher "
"stelle ich euch meine Stahlkolosse zur Verfügung und reite an Eurer Seite in "
"den Kampf! Für Alheirra!"

#. [message]: speaker=thesandir
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:483
msgid ""
"You cannot persist against Alheirra, bandits! We will defend our country to "
"death!"
msgstr ""
"Ihr könnt nicht gegen Alheirra bestehen, Banditen! Wir werden unser Land bis "
"zum Tod verteidigen!"

#. [message]: speaker=marshal
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:487
msgid "Nobody can stop us."
msgstr "Niemand kann uns aufhalten."

#. [message]: speaker=mlguard
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:491
msgid "Charge!"
msgstr "Angriff!"

#. [message]: speaker=thesandir
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:519
msgid "Rush forward!"
msgstr "Stürmt vor!"

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:529
msgid "And so the north was releived from the bandits."
msgstr "Und so wurde der Norden von den Banditen befreit."

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:532
msgid "Thesandir returned to Wizlud where he was welcomed by his folk."
msgstr ""
"Thesandir kehrte nach Wizlud zurück, wo er von seinem Volk begrüßt wurde."

#. [unit]: id=pihak, type=Cavalryman
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:546
msgid "Pihak"
msgstr "Pihak"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:559
msgid "Listen to the envoy."
msgstr "Höre dem Boten zu."

#. [message]: speaker=pihak
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/i.cfg:568
msgid ""
"My lord, the marshal of Alheirra thanks you on behalf of the whole nation "
"for your brave and altruistic commitment in this dark hour. Everyone would "
"have gave in seeing this superiority but you saved thousands' lives and also "
"Alheirra. This nation is in your debt eternally."
msgstr ""
"Mein Herr, der Marschall von Alheirra dankt Euch im Namen der gesamten "
"Nation für Euren mutigen und selbstlosen Einsatz in dieser dunklen Stunde. "
"Jeder hätte angesichts dieser Übermacht aufgegeben, aber ihr habt Tausende "
"Leben gerettet und ebenso Alheirra. Dieses Land steht auf ewig in Eurer "
"Schuld."

#. [scenario]: id=ii1
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:4
msgid "II"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: id=nelad, type=General
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:21 sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:114
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:192
msgid "Nelad"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: id=kelradir, type=Halberdier
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:33
msgid "Kelradir"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:46
msgid "Defeat Kelradir."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=nelad
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:59
msgid "What's up with you, old friend?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:63
msgid "Don't you talk to the king like this, you scum!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=nelad
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:67
msgid "What are you talking about, Kelradir?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=kelradir
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:71
msgid "Guards, kill this rioter. He's endangering the nation's safety."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:99
msgid ""
"After Nelad had defeated his old friend Kelradir, he went on a journey "
"through the nation to report to the marshal of Alheirra."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:102
msgid ""
"When he finally arrived, he was told the marshal had no time for this right "
"now so he would have to wait with his guards."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:105
msgid ""
"To find out more about the business taking place in Alheirra, Nelad sent out "
"a few guards to talk to civics. But to their surprise, the doors were shut "
"and locked although it was a good day to sell their goods. This made Nelad "
"even more worried about things."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:108
msgid ""
"So they went outside the town and camped near Jindaril for a while. But "
"suddenly some bandits appeared whose physical state was remarkably good. "
"Without a warning, they attacked."
msgstr ""

#. [side]: id=raider, type=Highwayman
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:126
msgid "Raider"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:137
msgid "Defeat the raider."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=raider
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:149
msgid "You must die, pig."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:177
msgid ""
"After Nelad's forces had won the struggle, he searched for something that "
"would indicate where they came from."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:180
msgid ""
"He found a scroll in an old, worn out leather bag. It said: 'Intruder at "
"Jindaril sector. -No convicts.'"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:183
msgid ""
"Nelad read the scroll again. Then he recognized the handwriting of the "
"marshal. His thoughts were not fast enough to remember the technique the "
"marshal called 'the False Positive'."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:186
msgid ""
"This technique assumed a first, medium heavy strike which the enemy could "
"scrape through, followed by a heavy but low-effort assault which would leave "
"no one alive."
msgstr ""

#. [side]: id=nemesis, type=Highwayman
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:204
msgid "Nemesis"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:217
msgid "Bring it to an end."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=nelad
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:229
msgid "Why does this happen? Why are you doing this? Why must I die?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=nemesis
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:233
msgid ""
"They always ask 'why'. You don't need to worry about it. It would exceed the "
"bounds of your neuronal abilities."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=nemesis
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:237
msgid ""
"You might think Alheirra is lost, but you are wrong. We know that we cannot "
"resist the marshal's army but at least we can cover our tracks before it is "
"too late."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=nemesis
#: sunkenstories/scenarios/ii.cfg:241
msgid ""
"That is why we must kill you. You are just a man on a giant draughtboard. "
"Today the victory is ours."
msgstr ""
